##### Setting Up the Lab for LFI 1

You can follow the full write-up that includes detailed setup instructions for the LFI 1 lab at the following link:

[LFI 1 Write-up on GitBook](https://skf.gitbook.io/asvs-write-ups/local-file-inclusion-1-lfi-1/lfi-1)

Alternatively, you can directly start the lab from the [SecureBy.Design platform](https://secureby.design) by deploying the lab environment, as shown in the image below:

![LFI Lab Deploy Button](/assets/gitbook/images/lfi-lab-deploy.jpeg)

You're all set to dive into the Local File Inclusion lab!
